      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like i'm dragging this weight around every single day for no reason. everyone keeps telling me \"it gets better\" or \"give it time\" but time is just more empty space. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. i'm just tired of being a ghost in this house.",
