      "content": "sometimes i look at his side of the bed and it feels more real than i do. like i'm just an extra, an afterthought that doesn't belong anymore. what's the point of pushing through all this just to sit in a room where nothing happens? it feels like i'm just stuck in a waiting room for a life that's already over.",
